It&#39;s almost like TPB&#39;s in comics, you need the physical game to get to the video game version most times but can you do the video first.  StarGate is trying it and from what I hear, they are going to release a third set on the computer but not the actual cards of it.  <br />
<br />
I&#39;d say gaming in most part is dead.  Even Magic will be dead within 4 years.  Hasbro doesn&#39;t want WOTC anymore and have been making them change many of their policies.  <br />
<br />
Unless you enjoy classic games like SW, ST, Rage, Overpower and so on, I wouldn&#39;t be investing in new games.  I&#39;m only Pre-ordering for the amount I pre-sold, I&#39;m not busting boxes anymore, it&#39;s not worth the time or money anymore.  <br />
